# ─── Frontend runtime env ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only required in production when frontend and backend are on different
# domains (e.g. frontend on Vercel, backend on Railway/Render).
#
# Leave unset in local dev if using Vite proxy.
# Example: VITE_API_URL=https://api.your-domain.com
#VITE_API_URL=https://api.example.com